asSub

public Type asSub(Symbol sym)
从类 Type 复制的描述
Return the least specific subtype of this type that starts with symbol sym. if none exists, return null. The least specific subtype is determined as follows: If there is exactly one parameterized instance of sym that is a subtype of this type, that parameterized instance is returned. Otherwise, if the plain type or raw type `sym' is a subtype of this type, the type `sym' itself is returned. Otherwise, null is returned.

类 Type.ClassType 中的 asSub

isCastable

public boolean isCastable(Type that)
从类 Type.ClassType 复制的描述
The rules for castability are extended to parameterized types as follows: (1) One may always cast to a supertype (2) One may cast to a subtype C<...> provided there is only one type with the subtype's class part, C, that is a subtype of this type. (This is equivalent to: C<...> = this.asSub(C). (3) One may cast an interface to an unparameterized class. (4) One may cast a non-final class to an unparameterized interface.

覆盖：
类 Type.ClassType 中的 isCastable

hasSameArgs

public boolean hasSameArgs(Type that)
从类 Type 复制的描述
Does this type have the same arguments as that type? It is assumed that both types are (possibly polymorphic) method types. Monomorphic method types "have the same arguments", if their argument lists are equal. Polymorphic method types "have the same arguments", if they have the same arguments after renaming all type variables of one to corresponding type variables in the other, where correspondence is by position in the type parameter list.

覆盖：
类 Type 中的 hasSameArgs
